        <abstract>
            <p>Regrets that JS has left the [Edinburgh] Botanic Garden and that [J. D.] Hooker is not in a position to secure a foreign appointment for him. Offers financial assistance on the grounds of science.</p> 
<p>Has sent JS a copy of the <hi rend="italic">Reader</hi>.</p> 
        </abstract>
